Why all dots are not blue?

ggplot(data = mpg) +
   geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy, shape = year))

 エラー: A continuous variable can not be mapped to shape

ggplot(data = mpg) +
   geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy, stroke = class))

 coords$stroke * .stroke でエラー:  二項演算子の引数が数値ではありません 

ggplot(data = mpg) +
   geom_point(mapping = aes(color = year)) +
   geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy))

 エラー: geom_point requires the following missing aesthetics: x, y

continuous value
